	color = { 0 0 0 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }

			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	color2 = { 255 255 255 }

			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Kyndecuf = {
	color = { 158 216 31 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Kyrbhyrtlis

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {

		color = { 254 167 53 }

		capital = c_Masorcholia

			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion

		ai_primary_priority = {
			if = {
				limit = {
					culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group

			NOT = {
			faith = {

			}
		}

		if = {
			limit = {

			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Hermigourncum = {
	color = { 50 50 50 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Kourdymene

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

e_Iaasosse = {
	color = { 185 234 127 }
	color2 = { 255 255 255 }
	capital = c_Diochytlia

	can_create = {
			NOT = {
			faith = {
				religion_tag = christianity_religion
				has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
			}
		}
	}

	ai_primary_priority = {
		if = {
			limit = {
				culture_group = culture_group:central_germanic_group
			}
			add = @correct_culture_primary_score
		}
	}

	k_Maropusatrea = {
		color = { 127 161 1 }

		capital = c_Diochytlia

		can_create = {
			NOT = {
				faith = {
					religion_tag = christianity_religion
					has_doctrine = doctrine_spiritual_head
				}
			}
		}

		ai_primary_priority = {
			if = {
				limit = {
